
For details of smartKONTROL, see here:
http://www.ciseco.co.uk/smartKONTROL.html

This is some test code to allow aSENSOR devices manufactured by Ciseco PLC
to be interrogated using ruby.

Instructions
============

First download and install the ruby-serialport library
http://rubyforge.org/projects/ruby-serialport/

now change to the ruby subdirectory and run:

ruby comm.rb

